for a group of five friends on Thursday.

00:00:10.153 --> 00:00:12.494
So, if we look over here,

00:00:12.494 --> 00:00:16.244
we can see that here on
this horizontal axis,

00:00:17.372 --> 00:00:19.366
when we're going from the left to right,

00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:21.098
it says hours of exercise,

00:00:21.098 --> 00:00:22.727
so half an hour, one hour,

00:00:22.727 --> 00:00:25.580
one and a half hours, two
hours, two and a half hours.

00:00:25.580 --> 00:00:28.152
And then, here it shows
hours of screen time.

00:00:28.152 --> 00:00:31.614
So, for example, it looks like Liu Yang

00:00:31.614 --> 00:00:33.941
did zero hours of exercise,

00:00:33.941 --> 00:00:38.287
